# Colors
This is the syntax for colors in pres:
- [*TYPE*/NUMBER/]{*TEXT*}

The three syntax elements are discussed below

# TYPE
The type of color to apply:
- *f* foreground color
- *F* bright foreground color
- *b* background color
- *B* bright background color

# NUMBER
A number between /0-7/ which denotes the color according to *ANSI*:
- *0* black
- *1* red
- *2* green
- *3* yellow
- *4* blue
- *5* magenta
- *6* cyan
- *7* white

# TEXT
The text
